class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc25816b67760c377110139bf6537514ec000bd","tid":205790,"uid":51123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T14:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傳說 google 可能會支援 swift 請問有冇人估機會大唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無乜可能, 成個 Memory Management 都唔同 <br />\n<br />\n除非Google 出 Native Android Development <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁樣就可以非開兩邊，一邊 JVM 一邊 Native <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8149e1edfc9f77c4abdb6ce2b4417df579beff","tid":205790,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>傳說 google 可能會支援 swift 請問有冇人估機會大唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無乜可能, 成個 Memory Management 都唔同 <br />\n<br />\n除非Google 出 Native Android Development <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁樣就可以非開兩邊，一邊 JVM 一邊 Native <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我感覺上個新聞係引人去寫swift<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fab25c94f345df2c03adc7f872df6ad3f1a7ad","tid":205790,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:25:11.000Z","msg":"啱啱研究緊<br />\n想玩埋anko<br />\n但個layout preview plugin同gradle撞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170bcf42834ed64377a2ce5945ebe0b0ea2e0db0","tid":205790,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"有時我諗<br />\n學呢d不如正正經經去寫返java<br />\nApps唔興都叫有底呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0018e170a75edb0ed42da9befe89fdb87f9ea8","tid":205790,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>傳說 google 可能會支援 swift 請問有冇人估機會大唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無乜可能, 成個 Memory Management 都唔同 <br />\n<br />\n除非Google 出 Native Android Development <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁樣就可以非開兩邊，一邊 JVM 一邊 Native <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我感覺上個新聞係引人去寫swift<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAndroid 由java 轉 swift 感覺會同當年Apple 出 Mac OS X 一樣, 成個OS完全唔同左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc62ce80458506c810c5e7da5448d9737636104","tid":205790,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:40:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時我諗<br />\n學呢d不如正正經經去寫返java<br />\nApps唔興都叫有底呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實java for android 呢兩年都大把野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nrxjava + retrofit + databinding 呢幾樣野而家應該基本要識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafd4a77ada3dc3ea79f684289d983c3f100b698","tid":205790,"uid":6801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有時我諗<br />\n學呢d不如正正經經去寫返java<br />\nApps唔興都叫有底呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實java for android 呢兩年都大把野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nrxjava + retrofit + databinding 呢幾樣野而家應該基本要識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nrxjava+retrofit真係基本野<br />\n做network call太有用<br />\ndatabinding既話kotlin都有extension做到"},{"pid":"bb52718528a0d93f75c8b6c424625bbeb6161900","tid":205790,"uid":34998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:39:43.000Z","msg":"最近有試玩 spek 做 testing<br />\n不過諗諗吓都係用返 junit 4 + kotlin 算<br />\n個 intellij branch coverage 廢咗，我都無乜心機再揾 jacoco 果啲去試效果啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKotlin 啲配套唔係好得，需要啲時間去改進<br />\ndokka for android gradle plugin 而家用唔到（好似係因為 android tool 出咗新版佢哋追唔切）<br />\nanko layout dsl 個 IDE plugin 裝完個 IDE 就會 crash，完全用唔到（我而家剩係用 common 果個 dependency）<br />\nspek 又唔係好夾到 IDE（雖然 spek 唔係真係官方出，但個 plugin 真係差過用 junit）<br />\ndagger2-android 果幾個 dependency 加咗上去開 proguard 又 build 唔到，完全唔知乜事<br />\n<br />\n不過就咁講寫嘅話 kotlin 係好過 java 嘅"},{"pid":"710f3748c78019adbef4877f83599424f5b6b4fe","tid":205790,"uid":34998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:43:59.000Z","msg":"kotlin出咗1.1.2，dagger-android-processor好似work返<br />\ndokka android 用0.9.14-eap-3又得返"},{"pid":"c4b5cc8aba298ad8ec1c467e403355158af81ae4","tid":205790,"uid":6801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:50:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>kotlin出咗1.1.2，dagger-android-processor好似work返<br />\ndokka android 用0.9.14-eap-3又得返</blockquote><br />\nproguard到？"},{"pid":"005b4546fc361178bee5237f0e77a8e97f86443a","tid":205790,"uid":34998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:57:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>kotlin出咗1.1.2，dagger-android-processor好似work返<br />\ndokka android 用0.9.14-eap-3又得返</blockquote><br />\nproguard到？</blockquote><br />\n咦，都係唔得，搞錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}